            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;I imagine the &lt;code&gt;for(int value : int_array) {/* loop content */}&lt;/code&gt; is slowest in your test because it is syntactically equivalent to &lt;code&gt;for(int i = 0; i &amp;lt; int_array.length; i++) {int value =  int_array[i]; /* loop content */}&lt;/code&gt;, which isn&apos;t what your test compares.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/889583/daiscog&quot; title=&quot;10,390 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;daiscog&lt;/a&gt;
